name: "Master Barber, Need I Say More??"
description:
This black cotton/polyester blend t-shirt for barbers is great for weekends at the shop and casual days. With a premium high quality feel and durability,our barber shirts are sure to leave a lasting impression for your customers.  

These shirts will advertise you and your business without you having to say a word!
